    Class and Description
    AbstractSimulator 
    DecoratorSimulator
    This class gives support for all common functionality in simulator decorators, according to Decorator pattern
    ISimulator
    This interface provides all common methods for all kind of simulator IMPORTANT: Classes which implement this interface or extend both DecoratorSimulator and Simulator should have only fields which implement java.io.Serializable.
    ISimulatorInfo
    An interface to get information about available simulators
